SUMMARY:YOGA IN NATURE™ at Apex Nature Park
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\nJoin us for a 60 minute slow vinyasa flow to yin yoga practice\, designed for beginners (to intermediate) AND first timers WELCOME.\nThe yoga practice (breath and asana) is infused with a connection to nature in order to help calm the mind and energize the body.\nYoga heals.\nNature heals.\nCost is $15/person payable by cash\nOR Venmo @Darlene-Genander (0862 if asked)\nOR PayPal dgenander@yogainnature.com\nAlso accepting payment with Zelle\nBring your yoga mat\, water\, towel or plastic liner for under your mat (if you want to protect it from ground/wet) or anything else you may use for your yoga practice.\nWEAR LAYERS\nHope to see you soon!
